Job Title:Senior Software Design Engineer (ADC), Online B2C Services Job Number:JO-1403-217329 Industry:Technology/Online/Online B2C Services Job Category/Function:Technology/Developer
About Our Client:
Our client is one of the first payment device manufacturers, with initial service offerings such as point-of-sale till date offering payment technology expertise, solutions and services that add value to the point of sale with merchant-operated, consumer-facing and self-service POS payment systems.
Job Description:
Job Responsibilities - Engage in requirements identification, development of software engineering specifications, solution analysis and design on a wide range of assignments including software development, maintenance, and application developer support. - Work with project managers and product teams to ensure on-time delivery. - Demonstrate understanding of the phases of systems analysis, the software development process, and/or functional engineering principles.
Qualifications:
The Successful Applicant - Bachelor's degree in computer science, electronics engineering or other related fields with at least 4 years of experience in Linux development or in payment industry - Incumbent should be comfortable to work in environment with minimum supervision. - Travelling will be required as per business needs.
